{
  "stem": "26728.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The camp was liberated, I think, on the 12th of April and the armored-- by an armored outfit.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were still fighting.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, there were still a lot of combat in there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So these guys that liberated the camp were there for two days, and then they went on, and another group of infantry came in and took over the camp and eventually, by the time we got there, the tankers were gone, with few exceptions.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There were still men-- the tankers were still in the towers.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But-- and they had military government people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "This guy-- the first one I met-- was a Jewish man who was from G-2, which was intelligence.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he spoke several languages.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he had been sent to kind of-- he was a second lieutenant-- to kind of get things organized, because it was very chaotic.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They hadn't done anything to the camp by the time we got there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When we got there, we landed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Command cars came out, got these officers, and they went into the camp with high-ranking other officers-- people who had been involved in the liberation-- colonels, brigadier generals, high-ranking officers.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now, the pilots were pretty much left to their own devices.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So what we would do would be to find some staff sergeant with a jeep and say, hey, take us into the camp.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What is all this?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so he would explain to us, this is Buchenwald concentration camp, a Nazi concentration camp where they kept all the Jews and the gypsies and the criminals and what have you.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He didn't know any more about it-- much more about it than we did.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So, we would-- we would-- you could-- but here's the thing that I want to emphasize about this.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
